      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the priest that maketh atonement therewith shall have it; who by offering it made atonement for the trespass of the person that brings it, as typical of the atonement by the sacrifice of Christ; he was to have all but what was burnt, for himself and his sons; though no doubt but other priests then on duty in the court ate with him. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
